2011-02-06 Thomas Pifer <zero456@gmail.com>

  * CMakeLists.txt: Removed unnecessary dependecy checks: Stjerm only needs GTK
  and VTE to build. Updated version needed to build Stjerm to GTK 2.22 and VTE
  0.26. Added CPack support so we can make tarballs through make package_source.
  (Though this means no xz archives for source builds until CMake adds support 
  for it.) This may eventually be used to also build the RPM and DEB files 
  directly.
  
  * README: Updated version needed to build Stjerm to GTK 2.22 and VTE
  0.26.
  
  * NEWS: Updated.
  
  * src/CMakeLists.txt: Updated and documented.
  
  * doc/CMakeLists.txt: Added. This installs stjerm's man page onto the system.
  
  
