2011-02-04 Thomas Pifer <zero456@gmail.com>

  * Begin new branch and version update for 0.15
  
  * src/config.c (conf_init): Removed '-v' as an option for version information
  as the GNU standard for version information is '--version' while '-v' is 
  usually reserved for verbose. 
  
